Set up an object as intel from its init attribute in the editor.
Basic version plus curator and scripted event handlers:

```sqf
[this] [call](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/call) BIS_fnc_initIntelObject;

if ([isServer](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/isServer)) then {
