	] [call](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/call) [BIS_fnc_setServerVariable](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/BIS_fnc_setServerVariable);

	*// Diary entry shared with (follows [BIS_fnc_MP](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/BIS_fnc_MP) target rules):*
	this [setVariable](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/setVariable) ["recipients", [west](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/west), [true](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/true)];

	*// Sides that can interact with the intel object:*
	this [setVariable](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/setVariable) ["RscAttributeOwners", [[west](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/west)], [true](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/true)];

	*// Register intel object with Zeus as curator editable (_zeus is the curator module):*
    _zeus [addCuratorEditableObjects](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/addCuratorEditableObjects) [[this], [false](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/false)];

	*// Add Zeus scripted event:*
	[_zeus, "IntelObjectFound", {[hint](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/hint) "Intel found"}] [call](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/call) [BIS_fnc_addScriptedEventHandler](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/BIS_fnc_addScriptedEventHandler);

	*// Add a scripted event that notifies all clients via [systemChat](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/systemChat) when the intel is found:*
	[
		this,
		"IntelObjectFound",
		{
			[params](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/params) ["", "_foundBy"];
			[private](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/private) _msg = [format](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/format) ["Intel found by %1", [name](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/name) _foundBy];
